
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-jiang--mpls-tp-ring-fd-00.txt'>
    <title>"MPLS TP Ring Fault Detection and Localization", Albert Jiang, Guoman Liu, Xuehui Dai</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-jiang--mpls-tp-ring-fd-00.txt</link>
    <description>This document describes fault detection and localization mechanism for MPLS TP ring network using dedicated control node and bidirectional periodical status OAM message. The mechanism takes advantage of ring topology and greatly reduces OAM sessions and messages among nodes in the ring.</description>
    <dc:date>2009-09-28T22:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
